      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[var(--ink)] leading-tight">What is an Integrator? Definition and Role in Your Organization with Key Responsibilities and EOS Context</h1>
      <p class="text-[var(--ink-mute)] mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">The Integrator is the operational counterpart to the Visionary, the person who turns strategy into execution and aligns every team toward shared goals. This guide defines the role, its responsibilities, how it differs from related positions, and how AI agents and meeting software amplify it.</p>
