      <figure>
        <img src="/public/blog/integrator-hero.jpg" alt="Collaborative team environment emphasizing the integral role of an Integrator in operational efficiency" loading="lazy" width="2048" height="1152">
        <figcaption>A collaborative team environment emphasizing the integral role of an Integrator in operational efficiency.</figcaption>
